review:
Doctor will be available when ever any emergency situation arises. In our experience once we faced a critical situation with our child's health , doctor himself was there to direct us to consult appropriate surgeon and by his spontaneous action only we saved our child. Your family is amongst my other families who trust, respect my opinion and I value your concerns about your kid's.
Regards
